<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM8.8">
<l>kārkālat teḻukiṉṟa kārmukilkāḷ vēṅkaṭattup</l>
<l>pōrkālat teḻuntaruḷip porutavaṉār pērcolli</l>
<l>nīrkālat terukkilam paḻavilaipōl vīḻvēṉai</l>
<l>vārkālat torunāḷtam vācakamtan taruḷārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O black clouds that rise in Vēṅkaṭam during the monsoon!</l>
<l>Will He not spare a word one day during [this] long time</l>
<l>to me who am falling like a beautiful old Yarcum leaf during the rainy season,</l>
<l>uttering the names of [the Lord] who graciously going [to the battlefield]</l>
<l rend="indent">and fought during wartime?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
